      "section_id": "s8",
      "section_path": [
        "A. Attracting attention",
        "4. Give users more control over sorting algorithms"
      ],
      "ordinal": 32,
      "text": "Users must be able to choose which features they want to use a platform for. The other functionalities are then not visible to them. The default should be that no functionalities are selected. The user can then choose the desired functionalities via an opt-in system.",
